        "startTime": 9881,
        "endTime": 13949,
        "slowStartTime": 14972,
        "slowEndTime": 21149
    },
    {
        "text": "1933: Wera Mahler found when it was acknowledged by others, it felt real in the mind.",
        "startTime": 14321,
        "endTime": 19024,
        "slowStartTime": 21632,
        "slowEndTime": 28761
    },
    {
        "text": "1982, Peter Gollwitzer wrote a whole book about this,...",
        "startTime": 19458,
        "endTime": 22009,
        "slowStartTime": 29337,
        "slowEndTime": 33238
    },
    {
        "text": "...and in 2009, he did some new tests that were published.",
        "startTime": 22136,
        "endTime": 25764,
        "slowStartTime": 33354,
        "slowEndTime": 38871
    },
    {
        "text": "It goes like this: 163 people across four separate tests.",
        "startTime": 26119,
        "endTime": 30577,
        "slowStartTime": 39328,
        "slowEndTime": 46091
    },
    {
        "text": "Everyone wrote down their personal goal.",
        "startTime": 31206,
        "endTime": 33126,
        "slowStartTime": 46959,
        "slowEndTime": 49914
    },
    {
        "text": "Then half of them announced their commitment to this goal to the room, and half didn't.",
        "startTime": 33511,
        "endTime": 38461,
        "slowStartTime": 50416,
        "slowEndTime": 57916
    },
    {
        "text": "Then everyone was given 45 minutes of work that would directly lead them towards their goal,...",
        "startTime": 39454,
        "endTime": 43427,
        "slowStartTime": 59331,
        "slowEndTime": 65366
    },
    {
        "text": "...but they were told that they could stop at any time.",
        "startTime": 43647,
        "endTime": 45517,
        "slowStartTime": 65620,
        "slowEndTime": 68500
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, those who kept their mouths shut worked the entire 45 minutes on average,...",
        "startTime": 46247,
        "endTime": 50714,
        "slowStartTime": 69520,
        "slowEndTime": 76296
    },
    {
        "text": "...and when asked afterward,...",
        "startTime": 50965,
        "endTime": 52324,
        "slowStartTime": 76597,
        "slowEndTime": 78711
    },
    {
        "text": "...said that they felt that they had a long way to go still to achieve their goal.",
        "startTime": 52597,
        "endTime": 55694,
        "slowStartTime": 79045,
        "slowEndTime": 83766
    },
    {
        "text": "But those who had announced it quit after only 33 minutes, on average,...",
        "startTime": 56327,
        "endTime": 60354,
        "slowStartTime": 84640,
        "slowEndTime": 90756
    },
    {
        "text": "...and when asked afterward, said that they felt much closer to achieving their goal.",
        "startTime": 60790,
        "endTime": 64797,
        "slowStartTime": 91335,
        "slowEndTime": 97420
    },
    {
        "text": "So if this is true, what can we do?",
        "startTime": 65357,
        "endTime": 67717,
        "slowStartTime": 98186,
        "slowEndTime": 101801
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, you could resist the temptation to announce your goal.",
        "startTime": 68521,
        "endTime": 72088,
        "slowStartTime": 102931,
        "slowEndTime": 108357
    },
    {
        "text": "You can delay the gratification that the social acknowledgement brings,...",
        "startTime": 72843,
        "endTime": 76759,
        "slowStartTime": 109414,
        "slowEndTime": 115364
    },
    {
        "text": "...and you can understand that your mind mistakes the talking for the doing.",
        "startTime": 77265,
        "endTime": 80776,
        "slowStartTime": 116047,
        "slowEndTime": 121389
    },
    {
        "text": "But if you do need to talk about something,...",
